Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召唤到异世界锡菲罗的三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克服了艾蒂露娜的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:02:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到传说的矿物艾斯古托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把艾斯古托铸成武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有创师普蕾西雅一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正回去普蕾西雅\N身处的沉默之森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍身成仁 普蕾西雅的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!? 地震!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在锡菲罗，魔物出现的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比发生地震的可能性更高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说不吉利的话啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这样吓别人的吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!你要好好管教它呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面震动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是锡菲罗开始崩溃的先兆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点!异世界的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果锡菲罗完全崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也不能返回原本的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即是说我一生都要住在这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没便利店没雪糕\N没书店的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想啊!绝对不想!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点!但你们要加倍小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默之森
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有谢加图的手下在埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果锡菲罗完全崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就不能返回原本的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去普蕾西雅那里吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近完全听不到魔物的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗开始崩溃了呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟导师古列夫所讲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死人了 最近的战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只是订制武器却不来取货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…导师古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上代创师跟你提过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!我听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗有危险时他们就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且叫我为他们铸造武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾，那时候来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，捉着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沉默之森
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个有魔物徘徊的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官谢加图\N把艾美诺公主软禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把艾斯古托\N铸成武器的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以让谢加图得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默之森是个可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而谢加图也不能插手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这间屋的门\N只有魔法骑士能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，如果谢加图认真起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也能像\N扭婴儿的手般轻易进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会死!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我用艾斯古托铸造武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给魔法骑士前，我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是创师真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能完成职责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，怎样和姐姐们玩好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔兽召唤!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚杜兰提，来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天玩个好玩的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子，把这个拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初难以相信\N她们是魔法骑士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢打扰我享受光\N给我的食物!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样惩罚你好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉长你的耳朵看能有多长好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿在这里即是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光!海!风!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 大家都没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们那些护甲…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾蒂露娜触摸艾斯古托时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们突然起了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些护甲是\N导师古列夫所赐的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫赐给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成长的护甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了和武器一起成长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，快来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要尽快为\N你们铸造最好的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是[创造室]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是铸造武器的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你铸造武器不需要工具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，需要的只是强大的意志力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿艾斯古托出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普…普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的武器是这样造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器…\N就是那样造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧，小海，小风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等，我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅你要完成你的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅你的职责是铸造武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，其他事就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是为了那样而来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你的话没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，之后的交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海，小风，去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没见一段短时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们变得很有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，我有我的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么怪物!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!再试一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法无效!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它看来每中一次\N魔法就能长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候不要佩服它啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的职责是铸造武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红电殛!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然魔法无效 用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器也无效!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜\N明明不能击败亚杜兰提
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却仍然拼命战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我困了，在亚杜兰提胜利前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们，它看来另有目标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是普蕾西雅小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要保护普蕾西雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区毛虫，为何走得这么快!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去正面引开它的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海小风你们就趁机攻击它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何剑会…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造室!普蕾西雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光!魔法无效啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用意志的力量阻止它!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能把普蕾西雅交给你!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真红电殛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气压很厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能救出普蕾西雅!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅，普蕾西雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海，我们也照做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯古托!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑呢…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一定要成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救锡菲罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那食物…很美味…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种糖我还有一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫…\N这样就行呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来!亚杜兰提!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样叫，那魔物也不会回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说什么亚杜兰提也会听从!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一叫，它就一定会回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它还活着就会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你自己的眼睛弄清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚杜兰提!亚杜兰提!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚杜兰提!你竟然变成这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会为你报仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放过…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你弄成这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅，我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会用你拼上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铸成的武器拯救锡菲罗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:46.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:59.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:11.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:24.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
